text: Not a busy place. You can find many cake and food places over here
Rice wine and lees were delicious but is a little pricey. Ordered online and was able to collect the next day from the store, fuss free.

A nice small neighborhood station.
The station is quite old for Singapore standard but it is clean and tidy. There is only an exit bound for each side of the main road. One of the exit is under the V Hotel Lavender and acces to the hotel entrance is fully covered so it is very comfortable. Right in the station entrance also have a small new hawker center which offer a reasonable price food.
Near mall and hotel. We can walk out from the station & find the mall easily
